flowchart TB
    subgraph RENDERER[Renderer computation domain]
        SRC[Lifecycle-resolved immutable sources]
        CFG[Contract-declared configuration]
        REN[Static renderer]
        PAYLOAD[Immutable payload]
        SRC --> REN
        CFG --> REN
        REN --> PAYLOAD
    end

    subgraph LIFECYCLE[Lifecycle mutation domain]
        RECOVER[Recover]
        PLAN[Immutable mutation plan]
        PREFLIGHT[Preflight guards]
        LOCK[Existing Workspace mutation lock]
        REVALIDATE[Under-lock revalidation]
        WRITE[Lifecycle atomic Write]
        VERIFY[Post-Write Verify]
        STATE[Acceptance and recovery state]
        RECOVER --> PLAN
        PAYLOAD --> PLAN
        PLAN --> PREFLIGHT
        PREFLIGHT --> LOCK
        LOCK --> REVALIDATE
        REVALIDATE --> WRITE
        WRITE --> VERIFY
        VERIFY --> STATE
    end

    subgraph WORKFLOW[Workflow integration domain]
        REF[Exact integration validation ref]
        BRANCH[Branch coordination]
        PR[Pull-request serialization]
        INTEGRATION[Integration-time guard revalidation]
        REJECT[Reject stale or unverifiable result]
        REGENERATE[Request lifecycle regeneration]
        REF --> BRANCH
        REF --> PR
        BRANCH --> INTEGRATION
        PR --> INTEGRATION
        INTEGRATION -->|guard mismatch| REJECT
        REJECT --> REGENERATE
    end

    subgraph PROTECTED[Repository integration domain]
        TARGET[Protected target ref]
    end

    STATE -->|candidate plan, state and bounded evidence| INTEGRATION
    INTEGRATION -->|all guards current and reproducible| TARGET
    REGENERATE -->|new exact ref and current authoritative inputs| RECOVER

    EVIDENCE[Bounded evidence]
    LIFECYCLE --> EVIDENCE
    WORKFLOW --> EVIDENCE

    EVIDENCE -. no lock, lease, acceptance or runtime authority .-> TARGET
    STATE -. not cross-ref serialization .-> WORKFLOW
    LOCK -. local only; not cross-branch or cross-PR .-> WORKFLOW
    WORKFLOW -. must not write target or acceptance state .-> WRITE
    REN -. no lock, workflow, state or write authority .-> LOCK
